## 🎯 Priority Outreach Targets (By Post)

> For each **outreach-worthy** post, identify 3-5 people who should know about it.
> 
> **Outreach-worthy** = you can imagine sending it to a specific person.
> This could be a long essay OR a short punchy take that directly engages someone's work.
> 
> **Not every post needs outreach** — aim for 3-5 outreach-worthy posts per week.

