## 📝 Response Post Opportunities

Recent posts from interesting people that merit substantive engagement:

| Author | Post | Our Angle | Priority |
|--------|------|-----------|----------|
| | | | |

**What makes a good response post**:
- Substantive engagement with their ideas (not just "great post!")
- Builds on, extends, or respectfully disagrees
- Creates a reason for them to engage back

